    <item>
      <title>Meta 淡化大选年人工智能虚假信息威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meta-leaders-say-they-re-not-seeing-ai-election-disinformation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 面临着巨大的压力，需要确保人工智能创建的社交媒体内容不会对今年的选举造成严重破坏。该公司的高层领导表示，他们的服务还没有看到这种情况发生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meta-leaders-say-they-re-not-seeing-ai-election-disinformation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:16:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员提出阻止美国技术流向对手的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/senators-propose-plan-to-stem-flow-of-us-tech-to-adversaries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位两党参议员提出了一项旨在更好地执行出口管制的法案，但迄今为止该法案未能阻止敏感技术流向美国对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/senators-propose-plan-to-stem-flow-of-us-tech-to-adversaries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
